Package com.example.goldencarrot.data.model.user

Class FacilityUserImpl

java.lang.Object
com.example.goldencarrot.data.model.user.UserImpl
com.example.goldencarrot.data.model.user.FacilityUserImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
User
public class FacilityUserImpl extends UserImpl
This class represents a user associated with a facility. It extends the UserImpl class and adds additional fields related to the facility such as facility name, location, and an image URL.

      public FacilityUserImpl(String email, String userType, String name, Optional<String> phoneNumber, Boolean administratorNotification, Boolean organizerNotification, Optional<String> facilityName, Optional<String> location, Optional<String> imageURL) throws Exception
      Constructs a FacilityUserImpl instance with the given parameters. This constructor initializes both the user-related and facility-related information.
      Parameters:
      email - the email address of the user
      userType - the type of user (e.g., "admin", "regular")
      name - the name of the user
      phoneNumber - the optional phone number of the user
      administratorNotification - flag indicating if the user should receive admin notifications
      organizerNotification - flag indicating if the user should receive organizer notifications
      facilityName - an optional name of the facility
      location - an optional location of the facility
      imageURL - an optional URL for the facility's image
      Throws:
      Exception - if any error occurs while setting the values
